{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002730/extras/StorepageHeader_Explore_1.gif?t=1731054321\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tall tales are often rooted in truth. After finding<i> The Tales of Violet Valley</i> book at your local library, you discover that the stories within are based on real events. You feel compelled to learn more. You do your research, you narrow down where the town is, and gather up your friends. It's time to explore.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002730/extras/Gameplay_Edit_2.gif?t=1731054321\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002730/extras/StorepageHeader_Town_1.gif?t=1731054321\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   Your group will explore different areas of the town. Each location hosts its own enemies and objectives while telling a small piece of a bigger story: what happened in Violet Valley? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002730/extras/Gameplay_Edit_1.gif?t=1731054321\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002730/extras/StorePageHeader4.2.gif?t=1731054321\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiplayer:</strong>\u00a0Tackle each location with up to 4 players. Solo play is supported, but teamwork is essential for the horror ahead.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Locations:</strong>\u00a0Start your journey with a set of locations patrolled by Robbie. Each of these areas features different objectives, enemies, and pacing. Some areas encourage running for it, while others require a sneakier approach. Hidden locations follow a different set of rules...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Objectives:</strong> Objectives are designed to get you further into a location.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Items:</strong> You're equipped with nothing but a flashlight and a couple of items you can use to distract Robbie. Lead him away from you and to your friend (we won't tell).</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002730/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731054321","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002730/page.bg.jpg?t=1731054321","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002730/ea9437e4ab9a3705ac04fd67172b33e6b5aeb29a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731054321","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002730/ea9437e4ab9a3705ac04fd67172b33e6b5aeb29a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731054321","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Depictions of mental health issues and psychological horror. "},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2002730/extras/StorepageHeader_Explore_1.gif?t=1731054321\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tall tales are often rooted in truth. After finding<i> The Tales of Violet Valley</i> book at your local library, you discover that the stories within are based on real events. You feel compelled to learn more. You do your research, you narrow down where the town is, and gather up your friends. It's time to explore.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st